### Auth — Register, Login, Social, Exchange, Forgot Password

### Register a new account
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Alex Parent",
  "email": "parent@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd1!"
}

###

### Login — copy token from response into http-client.env.json
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "parent@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd1!"
}

###

### Exchange short-lived code for JWT (social login callback)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/exchange
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "PASTE_CODE_HERE"
}

###

### Request password reset email
POST {{host}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "parent@example.com"
}
